messages.text: I know you told me not to talk about dead bodies anymore, but…
Yeah, well you have an autopsy assistant for a girlfriend, and this is huge
About two hours ago, this new body rolled in, but they don’t think it’s human
All these government officials have been filtering in
They found it in a field about 12 miles away.
I’m not. This place has been on lockdown
So like a little green man?
It’s not too farfetched, since we live near Area 51
I’m about to. They made me sign all these documents that I wouldn’t disclose any information
Okay, they’re making me stand in the back.
No. Or be near the table
Do you think you can send me a picture?
I was going to say maybe, but a bunch of armed guards just came in
YOU CAN’T JUST TELL ME X-FILES SHIT LIKE THIS AND DISAPPEAR!
I’m hiding in one of the cabinets in the lab
Right when my boss was about to cut into it, the alarm started going off
Somebody had entered where they didn’t belong
There was this bright light in the hall
I heard screaming from some of the guards
I don’t know. I’m scared. Just talk to me
Everything is going to be fine
I think they were coming back for it
No, they…its kind…like they didn’t want us interfering
So it was definitely an alien
It was pale blue. Two arms, three legs
I’ve never seen anything like it
I still feel like you’re messing with me
I NEED YOU TO BELIEVE ME RIGHT NOW
I just heard someone get thrown in the hall
I heard yelling, and a thud
Is there an air duct in the room you might be able to escape out of?
Oh my God Jason, something opened the door
Maybe it’s a guard just checking the area out
Just sit still and they will go away
Just stay quiet, I’m jumping in the car and speeding over
Okay, but remember that story about that guy Abe?
The one who showed up naked in a field saying he’d been abducted?
The things he said they did were terrible
It’s not going to happen to you
He’s telling me to come out
Does it look like your Dad
I think that’s a bad idea
I’m almost on my way there.
That can’t be your Dad Kim
Ask him what he wants first
He says he wants to show me something
Bullshit. Ask him to verify something that only he would know
He says he’s here, because we’re in danger, and he wants to take me to safety
He said he didn’t really die, but they took him to safety
And have been taking us in groups
What if it really is him!?
You just told me you brought in an alien as a cadaver
If that’s true, then I think you are trying to be fooled here
Kim, there’s a huge spacecraft above your building. It’s just hovering there
They have things gated off, with more armed guards
I’m going to try to drive around the back way
If you can manage to get out, escape through the back, and I’ll get you
I’m here. We’re talking. It’s my Dad
He said that you will soon believe too
He asked if you see anyone on the hill
There is someone standing in the distance
Yeah. If you’re too scared, just don’t get out of your car
This must be some weird dream or something
It’s not a dream. They want to save us
GET AWAY FROM THE MAN YOU’RE TALKING TO
This thing that pretended he was my Grandpa just tried to tear me out of my car
His eyes glowed red!  THAT IS NOT YOUR DAD
I’m not wrong! GET OUT OF THERE
He just said that’s it’s too late for all of us
There are more of those ships flying in
